<html>
	<head>
		<title>Sotonopoly API - RequestHandler</title>
	</head>
	
	<body>
		<h1>Game</h1>
		<a href='index.html'>Back to menu</a>
			<p>This class models a game instance. Each game running on the server will instantiate a <i>Game</i> object. Classes <i>Player</i>, <i>EventCard</i> and <i>Building</i> should be children of a <i>Game</i> object. This class has no methods available; all data processing occurs in the <i>GameUpdater</i>.</p>
			<p>Datastore model entity. Inherits from <i>Game</i> entity.</p>
			
		<h3>turn (integer)</h3>
			<p>Stores which player's turn it is by matching this value to a player with the same turnNumber field. This is -1 if the game has not yet started.</p>
			<p>Default value: -1</p>
			<p>Required? Yes.</p>
			
		<h3>pieces (list&lt;String&gt;)</h3>
			<p>Stores the names (also used as the id for rendering purposes by the client) of pieces available in the game.</p>
			<p>Default value: ["mortarboard", "dolphin", "book", "glass"]</p>
			<p>Required? Yes.</p>
			
		<h3>colours (list&lt;String&gt;)</h3>
			<p>Stores the hex values for colours available to players in the game.</p>
			<p>Default value: ["FF0000", "19A82C", "0000FF", "FFE303"]</p>
			<p>Required? Yes</p>
		
		<h3>inProgress (boolean)</h3>
			<p>True - the game has started as in progress</p>
			<p>False - the game is yet to start</p>
			<p>Default value: False</p>
			<p>Required? Yes</p>
		
		<h3>rollRemaining (boolean)</h3>
			<p>/* TODO */</p>
			<p>Default value: True</p>
			<p>Required? Yes</p>
			
		<h3>numRolls (integer)</h3>
			<p>/* TODO */</p>
			<p>Default value: 0</p>
			<p>Required? Yes.</p>
			
		<h3>lastDiceTotal (integer)</h3>
			<p>/* TODO */</p>
			<p>Default value: 0</p>
			<p>Required? Yes.</p>
					
	</body>
</html>